verses.text_plain: The earth is the Lord’s, and the fulness thereof; the world, and they that dwell therein.
verses.verse_html: 1The earth is the Lord’s, and the fulness thereof; the world, and they that dwell therein.

verses.text_plain: For he hath founded it upon the seas, and established it upon the floods.
verses.verse_html: 2For he hath founded it upon the seas, and established it upon the floods.

verses.text_plain: Who shall ascend into the hill of the Lord? or who shall stand in his holy place?
verses.verse_html: 3Who shall ascend into the hill of the Lord? or who shall stand in his holy place?

verses.text_plain: He that hath clean hands, and a pure heart; who hath not lifted up his soul unto vanity, nor sworn deceitfully.
verses.verse_html:
4He that hath clean hands, and a pure heart; who hath not lifted up his soul unto vanity, nor sworn deceitfully. ▼
▼ He…: Heb. The clean of hands

footnotes.body_text: ▼ He…: Heb. The clean of hands
footnotes.body_html: ▼ He…: Heb. The clean of hands

verses.text_plain: He shall receive the blessing from the Lord, and righteousness from the God of his salvation.
verses.verse_html: 5He shall receive the blessing from the Lord, and righteousness from the God of his salvation.

verses.text_plain: This is the generation of them that seek him, that seek thy face, O Jacob. Selah.
verses.verse_html:
6This is the generation of them that seek him, that seek thy face, O Jacob. Selah. ▼
▼ O Jacob: or, O God of Jacob

footnotes.body_text: ▼ O Jacob: or, O God of Jacob
footnotes.body_html: ▼ O Jacob: or, O God of Jacob

verses.text_plain: Lift up your heads, O ye gates; and be ye lift up, ye everlasting doors; and the King of glory shall come in.
verses.verse_html: 7Lift up your heads, O ye gates; and be ye lift up, ye everlasting doors; and the King of glory shall come in.

verses.text_plain: Who is this King of glory? The Lord strong and mighty, the Lord mighty in battle.
verses.verse_html: 8Who is this King of glory? The Lord strong and mighty, the Lord mighty in battle.

verses.text_plain: Lift up your heads, O ye gates; even lift them up, ye everlasting doors; and the King of glory shall come in.
verses.verse_html: 9Lift up your heads, O ye gates; even lift them up, ye everlasting doors; and the King of glory shall come in.

verses.text_plain: Who is this King of glory? The Lord of hosts, he is the King of glory. Selah.
verses.verse_html: 10Who is this King of glory? The Lord of hosts, he is the King of glory. Selah.
